('22','8','1','','0','',NULL,'','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　    近来很多人问我们，本周有活动吗。车加车网俱乐部经过实地探路、踩点，终于可以斩钉截铁的说：有！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　本周日我们到许亭水库来场聚会party~吧~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　见见那些平时自驾群里(QQ群号：285381306)聊的挺high，却从未谋面的；见见刚刚聊的还挺起劲，一说“请客吃饭”就潜水的……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　大家一起烧烤，吃吃喝喝，聊聊人生，谈谈理想。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　你以为只是这样？NO！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font